pageProduct.name: Swisse Ultiboost Evening Primrose Oil 200 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

SWISSE ULTIBOOST EVENING PRIMROSE OIL is a premium quality formula that provides a rich source of gamma linolenic acid (GLA) to help relieve inflammation, maintain healthy skin, and support general health and wellbeing.

Anti-inflammatory: Evening primrose oil is a rich source of GLA, a long-chain fatty acid to help relieve inflammation.

Women's Health: Research suggests that women with premenstrual syndrome (PMS) may have low levels of GLA. Evening primrose oil is a source of GLA for the maintenance of good health.

Skin Health: Evening primrose oil contains GLA to help maintain healthy skin.

Size: 200 Tablets

Warnings

If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

Ingredients

Each Capsule Contains: Evening Primrose Oil:
Gamma-Linolenic acid 100 mg

Contains soya beans & sulfites.

No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg, artificial colours or flavours.

Allergen Free From: Artificial Colours| Artificial Flavours| Egg| Gluten| Lactose| Yeast

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE -
ADULT DOSAGE: Two capsules, three times daily, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C.
